  • Method Details

    • fromSpotify

      private static TrackMetadata fromSpotify(String sourceId)
      Creates TrackMetadata from a Spotify music track. If there's a problem retrieving the metadata, null will be returned.
      Parameters:
      sourceId - The Spotify track ID
      Returns:
      A TrackMetadata describing the music track, which may be null

    • fromYouTube

      private static TrackMetadata fromYouTube(String sourceId)
      Creates TrackMetadata from a YouTube music track. Note that this method doesn't verify that the provided video ID is in fact for a music track. If there's a problem retrieving the metadata, null will be returned.
      Parameters:
      sourceId - The YouTube track ID
      Returns:
      A TrackMetadata describing the music track, which may be null

    • fromMusicSource

      public static TrackMetadata fromMusicSource(MusicSource source, String sourceId)
      Creates TrackMetadata from a music source and ID. If the music source is Unknown, or there's a problem retrieving the metadata, null will be returned.
      Parameters:
      source - The MusicSource to get the metadata from
      sourceId - The music track ID
      Returns:
      A TrackMetadata describing the music track, which may be null
